{"tid":1246660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果要求美國政府放棄對更多從中國輸美的商品徵收關稅","createTime":"2019-06-20T22:56:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T13:28:15.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6b9a82163adef3867684feef1030453dd33857cb","tid":1246660,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T22:56:09.000Z","msg":"蘋果要求美國政府放棄對更多從中國輸美的商品徵收關稅<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1464117-20190621.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1464117-20190621.htm&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ransg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=2be2a66d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1464117-20190621.htm&h=6436681c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1464117-20190621.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國再有大企業向總統特朗普政府施壓，要求放棄對更多從中國輸往美國的商品，徵收關稅的計劃。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果公司在政府網站貼文，指出政府建議將蘋果旗下的手機、平板電腦及電腦等，在中國生產後再輸往美國的商品徵收關稅，假如落實，將減低蘋果對美國經濟的貢獻，損害公司在全球的競爭力。蘋果又說，政府不應該推進對另外總值3千億美元中國商品，加徵最高25%關稅的計劃。<br />\n<br />\n早前有報道說，蘋果打算重整供應鏈，要求主要供應商，評估將一成半至三成產能撤離中國，轉移到東南亞，會對成本效益構成多大影響。"},{"pid":"56e4c18d45b835b90ce5411f5e397c7976e348c9","tid":1246660,"uid":35842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T22:57:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wweBR6Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwweBR6Q.png&h=279578dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"81e707f2b600510fd2db4b11699980ba6f80e964","tid":1246660,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:28:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}